defaultQuestion 31: defaultDo you think habitat banking should be allowed? Do you think a provider must show intent to create a habitat bank to be allowed to sell it as an 
defaultoffset? Do you think habitat banks should be “retired” if they are not used to provide an offset? If so, after 
