defaultYes it should and for the reasons given.  We suggest that an obligation to show intent is a prima facie an unnecessary imposition and this section of the consultation reads a little like it is trying to create obstacles. 
defaultThe imperative should 
defaultbe for the landowner 
defaultto improve the biodiversity and 
